    "type": "message",
    "text": "Welcome! It sounds like you have some unique perspectives -- a \"blue thought\" in a \"pink plane\". I hope this group is able help you discover the \"blue plane\" you are looking for (and develop whatever tools or approach will make that plane visible). ... If I'm not making sense, I'll refer you to this recent post of mine:\n\n<https://futureofcoding.slack.com/archives/C5T9GPWFL/p1552797651357800?thread_ts=1552755024.352300&amp;cid=C5T9GPWFL>\n\nI (and surely others here) are hoping to do something similar with programming or computing.",
