    "type": "message",
    "text": "Hi nagle! I think I saw your name come up before. I was working in Dan Ingalls' group on Lively at YCR HARC but I worked on stlightly different but related topics for my PhD (see link above). I'm still trying to follow the work of Bret Victor and Jonathan Edwards, etc. By the way, Coda sounds pretty cool. I have to check it out at some point.",
