    "client_msg_id": "03e05558-4737-4e9a-9b0e-acc11e3f7c5f",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "hi <@UFPRPSA4S>! my name's nagle. where are you based?\n\nI studied pure math and algebraic topology as well in school! i think it's really relevant to the work here -- the visceral knack for what good thinking is and isn't it.\n\ncurious if you've come across alan citing the hadamard study that only 30% of mathematicians thinking symbolically and the other big way are kinaesthetic and in imagery? he quotes einstein talking about feeling the curves of space-time in his back.",
    "user": "UGMH4H202",
